arteel said in a statement that cost cutting measures are being carried out as planned .
the stock market in paris welcomed the announcement by arca , saying that the shares of arca had risen 16.91 percent at the beginning of the afternoon session , reporting 6.5 euros per share .
basko , analyst of gay securities , said , " the repair of the sales figures for the fourth quarter is particularly unexpected . "
