( afp report from seoul ) south korean officials said that north korea said today that it has no intention of producing nuclear weapons .
" north korea stresses that it has no intention of producing nuclear weapons , " said lee feng - chao , spokesman for the south korean delegation .
in a press briefing on the one - hour - long formal talks , lee said the north korean delegation made the above statement following south korea 's urging the pyongyang regime to abandon its nuclear ambitions .
" south korea stresses that if the nuclear issue is not resolved , the entire north - south korean relationship will certainly be unable to move forward , " said lee feng - chao .
