the focus of the south - north ministerial talks this time is on reconciliation and humanitarianism . however , as a traditional ally of the united states , south korea has said that seoul authorities have decided to take this opportunity to express the international community 's concern over the nuclear deadlock .
north korea said the nuclear standoff was a bilateral issue only involving the united states , and intervention by other countries would only complicate the issue .
