xinhua news agency , baghdad , february 4 ( reporters wang bo , liang youchang ) - spokesman of the un weapons inspection group , zhulonghong , said in a press release on the 4 th that inspectors found another empty chemical warhead during an inspection of a suspicious spot in iraq that day .
the empty chemical warhead was found during an inspection of a drug depot in the northern suburbs of baghdad , zahiro said .
the warhead was affixed with a label , and was intact .
he said the warhead was similar to the 12 empty chemical warheads found by inspectors in an arms depot in southern iraq on january 16 .
soon after the inspectors found the empty chemical warheads , the iraqi side announced that four similar warheads were found in the taj region and handed them over to the inspectors .
when reporting to the security council on january 27 , blix , chairman of the un commission for verification , monitoring , and inspection , said that the iraqi government should take the initiative to give an account of these air chemical warheads in its arms report , instead of seeking them by inspectors .
inspectors also inspected seven locations near baghdad on the same day , including a water purifier , an agricultural chemical factory , two missile factories , and a center used to develop chemical weapons .
on the 4 th , inspectors in the northern iraqi city of mosul inspected a sugar factory and an yeep production plant .
the shanghai police confirmed that the two french planes were turkish men
xinhua news agency , shanghai , february 10 ( by yang jinzhi and yang pyong ) by fingerprint comparison , the shanghai police confirmed that the two men who crashed from the french airline air route a112 on january 23 were turkish residents , respectively 20 - year - old karadayi and 19 - year - old omar .
at 10:58 on the morning of 23 january , the shanghai municipal public security bureau made a report to the police . the report said that an air crash occurred in shengang village , old port town , south huichun . two foreigners fell on board a plane that was flying from the south to the north and prepared to land .
after on - the - spot investigation and investigation , the shanghai police promptly appraised the dead and confirmed that they had crashed from the arrival cabin of the fd112 passenger plane through the air . this conclusion has been affirmed by air france .
since then , the shanghai police have successively carried out cooperation and investigation with the french consulate general , the turkish consulate general , and the police of the two countries .
in early february , based on the remains at the scene of the two victims and the information provided by the turkish police about suspected victims ' fingerprints , identity cards , and so on , the shanghai police confirmed the identity of the two victims after technical comparison and finally confirmed their identity .
