the title of " china daily necessities production base " is a new town of the province , a new town located in the central part of nan'an city , the hometown of a national hero , and a coastal economic development zone in southern fujian .
the town was founded in 1999 . it has 61 square kilometers of land and 11 administrative villages with a population of 45,000 . it also has over 20,000 compatriots living abroad and hong kong , macao , and taiwan compatriots .
a complete industrial chain led by daily necessities has now been formed in the province 's new town .
there are more than 70 daily necessities enterprises in the entire province , with fixed assets reaching more than 300 - million yuan . they are engaged in production of daily necessities and supply and marketing cooperatives of more than 11,000 people , and annual export values of nearly 200 - million yuan .
the main products include various kinds of plastic film packaging bags , color bags , matching products for daily necessities , and women 's health scarves , baby trousers , food tissue , silk fabrics , children 's outdoor products , etc. products of several hundred varieties and up to 1,000 different specifications are sold throughout the country , as well as countries and regions in the united states , canada , europe , and southeast asia .
in 2002 , the output value of the day - to - day manufacturing industry in this town reached 500.4 billion yuan , accounting for 70 percent of the industrial output value of the whole town and paying industrial and commercial taxes of 14.08 million yuan , accounting for 67.1 percent of the total tax revenue in the entire town .
