xinhua news agency , united nations , february 11 ( reporter guo lijun ) the french permanent mission to the united nations released an unofficial proposal to the security council members on the 11th .
france suggests doubling the number of formal personnel performing weapons inspection missions in iraq in the near future and gradually increasing the number of inspectors to three times the current level .
