xinhua news agency , shenyang , february 16 ( reporter : shi qingwei ) - japan bell network corporation signed an agreement a few days ago with the management committee of shenyang city 's wenan new region to establish a joint venture , planning to invest 3 - billion japanese yen for the development of visual network telephony in the new south china region .
according to presentations , the first phase construction project of this joint venture is scheduled to be completed between april 2003 and march 2005 , and by 2005 , the number of staff and workers of the enterprise will reach 3,000 , and will become an important research and development base for the hardware and software of the visual network in north china .
experts concerned believe that china 's network telephony technology is still at the research and development stage , while japan 's bell network corp . is leading the world in this field . this project has a better development prospect in china .
founded in 1989 , the japan bell network corporation is a newly emerging it corporation in japan . it is mainly engaged in the development , production , and network communications services of computer network hardware and software . last year , its sales volume was 12.4 - billion yen .
